{"tid":1652793,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[正視聽] 蓮塘送中之路? 笑死人","createTime":"2019-10-13T20:35:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-15T07:21:50.000Z","uid":62063,"like":99,"dislike":137,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"bd3328eaf626477e7dc7b68c115b46679e38c6b5","tid":1652793,"uid":62063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T20:35:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/squuXVb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsquuXVb.png&h=d396de8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咩地底有兩條路真係得啖笑<br />\n個post重要有千幾正皮<br />\n好明顯睇到係移位<br />\n人哋crop嗰一細忽出嚟就信曬又唔FC<br />\n個shape同附近啲路一模一樣㗎大佬<br />\n<br />\n有啲又話運動場個位啱就代表冇移位問題<br />\n電話本身, 地圖, 訊號接收...<br />\nA冇事唔代表B都一樣標得啱<br />\n假設某個牌子電話/地圖app出錯就會集體移位<br />\n咁冇問題嗰啲當然會標得啱<br />\n<br />\n我相信兩地有秘道絕對唔出奇<br />\n但唔係呢度囉<br />\n要查都查返調景嶺HKDI同埋石硤尾單嘢先啦<br />\n<br />\n仲有好心咪唔啱聽就話人係5毛/黑警<br />\n人哋都係見到有問題先出聲啫"},{"pid":"8e646edbf5a87a5e4f2953073628ba993cd88cbc","tid":1652793,"uid":62063,"like":7,"dislike":6,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T20:37:32.000Z","msg":"FC啦好嗎"},{"pid":"586313576a7f083624d38d3a9669147278ad1a80","tid":1652793,"uid":62063,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T20:38:05.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"9cd4693e3a54d4603177dfe2d7e0f5f65d071fb3","tid":1652793,"uid":62063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T20:38:16.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"7bde79583146a7e96c8fd5bc8e9d670281d50572","tid":1652793,"uid":62063,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T20:38:26.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"703946bf99e745239c78a4a5e074699c4c44b2a5","tid":1652793,"uid":62063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T20:38:36.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"00c7a4fa25fb70e502f0acbf93c4aa3f0846ecfd","tid":1652793,"uid":62063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T20:38:46.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"c9df5a5fcee51a5f1ca22fd8b6ff7a12fa23fda4","tid":1652793,"uid":62063,"lik