 />\n電話本身, 地圖, 訊號接收...<br />\nA冇事唔代表B都一樣標得啱<br />\n假設某個牌子電話/地圖app出錯就會集體移位<br />\n咁冇問題嗰啲當然會標得啱<br />\n<br />\n我相信兩地有秘道絕對唔出奇<br />\n但唔係呢度囉<br />\n要查都查返調景嶺HKDI同埋石硤尾單嘢先啦<br />\n<br />\n仲有好心咪唔啱聽就話人係5毛/黑警<br />\n人哋都係見到有問題先出聲啫"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T21:35:46.000Z","msg":"都唔係GPS 問題<br />\n係中國地圖格式問題<br />\n所以啲路疊起晒<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=L9Di-UVC-_4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DL9Di-UVC-_4&d=0ZNtUZ9Qk1f13jNJdsSeN8v4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=9f320d7e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=L9Di-UVC-_4</a><br />\n<br />\nTLDW:<br />\n國際係WGS84 格式<br />\n但中國係GCJ02<br />\n但GCJ02 係加咗隨機化座標入去<br />\n只有中國指定十四間國企先可以用隨機化咗嘅地圖<br />\n<br />\nStrava 係用Google Maps <br />\nGoogle Maps 用WGS84嘅係衛星圖<br />\n但配上咗 GCJ02 嘅中國街道圖<br />\n所以中國啲路同香港啲路疊住晒"},{"pid":"49a151b3be80f096d4cf4b6d53b9d10c91f69553","tid":1652793,"uid":62063,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T21:36:28.000Z","msg":"我見到隔離post啲人就好似見到話識用airdrop/telegram背後一定係有外國勢力嗰啲一樣"},{"pid":"6bfbf867c7d52033154ae69a34ecf27a048e44d1","tid":1652793,"uid":89514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T21:46:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"561663ee5ece13c674e9ceb8e5508ee291e31bed","tid":1652793,"uid":62063,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6bfbf867c7d52033154ae69a34ecf27a048e44d1","tid":1652793,"uid":89514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee815f5477659b97aa2733d7b4ce840229fd99d1","tid":1652793,"uid":62063,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T21:15:53.000Z","msg":"[震驚]船灣淡水湖底有秘道<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c1FNKUT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc1FNKUT.png&h=d6e30735&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T21:46:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T21:47:58.000Z","msg":"講緊開post張圖定邊張？"},{"pid":"8e848a78f3aa8acbb7e